Text: RE Status of the Old Office at HelsinkiStacey Thank You for the report and for visiting us The old office is still vacant and we are paying I proposed today for Neil AustinLondon and Thorstein JenssenOslo that we should take an other property consultant to carry the task beside HealeyBaker Our landlord at the new premises is Regus wwwreguscom This arrangement is fine and easy to leave We are staying here for years then apartment type or OsloLondon Some minor notes to Your very good draft Ms Heidi Sieppi moved to Oslo today June th to work there for months Yes Regus Offices Small cameras is a very good idea each in Finland To office profile I would like to add Helsinki offices one task is to recruit from Finland for Enron On the business control side On our expense claims are travelling and minor marketing expenses Sincerely Juhani Original Message From White Stacey Sent June To Aalto Juhani Subject Status of the Old Office Juhani Please see the attached Preliminary Finland Doorstep Review What is the status with the old office Let me know if anything does not read correctly I left the office pamphlet at my house is it Remus Hope all is well in Finland Thank you again for all your help and information Thanks Stacey File Preliminary Helsinki Doorstep Reviewppt
One good presentation from NordpoolStacey Here is some extra info from Scandinavia and Europe Best wishes Juhani
